              "body": "````suggestion\n for KV cache transfer, two-sided SEND/RECV for expert parallelism dispatch), and\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 23,
              "body": "````suggestion\nThe DUT boundary for all measurements in this document is defined as the NIC-to-NIC\nEthernet fabric segment \u2014 specifically, the path from the point of packet\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 25,
              "body": "````suggestion\nat the destination NIC Ethernet port.\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 27,
              "body": "````suggestion\nIntra-node transfer segments (NVLink GPU-to-GPU, PCIe/CXL GPU-to-NIC) are explicitly\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 34,
              "body": "````suggestion\nThe document does NOT address benchmarking of individual accelerator (GPU/XPU) compute\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 57,
              "body": "````suggestion\n  PCIe/CXL (intra-node, out of scope as DUT); (2) NIC-to-NIC: Ethernet fabric\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 62,
              "body": "````suggestion\n  latency and throughput exclusively.\n  When end-to-end measurements are reported (e.g., TTFT decomposition), the intra-node\n  segments MUST be labelled separately.\n````",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T18:21:14Z"
            }
          ]
        },
